@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_iyazbo(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.sin(0.30)
    v1 = 0.18
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.sin(wp.exp(v1 + 0.36)))
    v1 = 0.92
    v1 = wp.sin((tmp * (v0 + 0.30 - tmp + 0.52)))
    v1 = ((wp.exp(v2 + 0.24) / wp.exp(v0 + 0.38)) + (wp.sin(tmp + 0.31) * v0))
    v0 = (0.30 / (0.16 / (v1 + 0.54 * v2 + 0.54)))
    data[tid] = v0
